sequenceDiagram

participant ADMIN as Admin / IBX BP
participant UI
participant BFF
participant SERVICE as Innovation Service
participant OPENTEXT as MSIL OpenText DMS
participant AIWF as AI Workflow (Doc Parser)
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

%% -------------------------------
%% STEP 1: Create Draft Portfolio (Details Tab)
%% -------------------------------

ADMIN->UI: Enter Portfolio Details
UI->BFF: Save Draft (Details Tab)

BFF->SERVICE: validate + save draft
SERVICE->PRIMARYDB: insert portfolio (Draft)
SERVICE->PRIMARYDB: insert stages + config

BFF->UI: Draft Saved

%% -------------------------------
%% STEP 2: Upload Ringi Document (OpenText Integration)
%% -------------------------------

ADMIN->UI: Upload Ringi Document
UI->BFF: upload document

BFF->OPENTEXT: store document
OPENTEXT->BFF: document_id + metadata

%% AI-based extraction (non-deterministic, async capable)
BFF->AIWF: extract ringi metadata
AIWF->BFF: extracted fields

BFF->SERVICE: update ringi metadata
SERVICE->PRIMARYDB: save ringi details

BFF->UI: Auto-populate Ringi Details tab

%% -------------------------------
%% STEP 3: Configure Evaluation Model
%% -------------------------------

ADMIN->UI: Define evaluation questions & weights
UI->BFF: save evaluation config

BFF->SERVICE: validate weights + rules
SERVICE->PRIMARYDB: insert evaluation config

SERVICE->PRIMARYDB: calculate subtotal & grand total

BFF->UI: Show calculated totals